|-
| [[File:Sweet_Apple.png|20px]] [[Sweet Apple]] || 20 [[File:Red_Shard_Updated.png|20px]] [[Red Shard|Red Shards]] <br> 30 [[File:Rose_Shard_Updated.png|20px]] Rose Shards || 1250 {{Questpoints}}
|}

For more information on how one can purchase these items, please check the [[Shard Trader]] page.

==Acquisition==
Rose Shards can be found in the [[Underground]], traded for with the [[Berry Master|Hoenn Berry Master]], and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

